{"tid":1482134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家都已經二十一世紀 唔好咁迷信 個天落唔落雨 關地上面既人咩事?","createTime":"2019-08-18T03:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T08:35:37.000Z","uid":30791,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4de585d29236be239beea7d8b1a29fca046f0980","tid":1482134,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人在做 天沒有在看<br />\n有因果 但係無報應<br />\n死後落唔落地獄我唔知<br />\n你想確保對方生不如死 就只有靠自己</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"56ed35ef71ec641f557ee72c90358016944c3031","tid":1482134,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:59:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">事在人為</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"73a5da7f4d44907c7ca86f70f354dd1452235646","tid":1482134,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nThere is no heaven<br />\nNo hell below us<br />\nAbove us only sky<br />\nImagine all the people<br />\nLiving for today<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3a09c607a9bf1d7faf6a96d5ab145a1524311347","tid":1482134,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所謂報應 所謂天 就係正義既代理人<br />\n給反抗不了的人 用來安慰自己<br />\n無論壞人做左咩壞事 總有一個高於一切的定律去整治壞人<br />\n這只是一種讓自己好過一點的說法<br />\n現實係 如果沒有人去執行正義<br />\n大部份壞人都可以逍遙自在<br />\n那些不幸的 與天地無關 與正義無關<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"98915d2c9b0fcd72fa548a466c81994b98eb61de","tid":1482134,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=